snippet.title: Operation CrossCounter Trailer
snippet.description:
Operation CrossCounter is a new cross-platform multiplayer co-op RPG for Android, iOS and the web. Players will group up into groups of 3 and take on invading hordes of robots, all rendering in some pretty nice 3D visuals.

No official release date for Android has been announced, only that it is coming in the very near future. More details over at our site: http://bit.ly/N0V7k4
